byomkesh bakshi is a 2015 indian bengali mystery thriller film directed by dibakar banerjee and produced by pradip churiwal . the film stars konkona sen sharma and raima sen in the lead roles . the film is based on the novel byomkesh bakshi by sharadindu bandyopadhyay . the film is based on the novel byomkesh bakshi by sharadindu bandyopadhyay .